2026-05-16T22:04:20.7296342Z 271            Harden Google Play Billing's proxy activities so the system
2026-05-16T22:04:20.7297016Z 272            cannot restore them from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-16T22:04:20.7297376Z 273            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-16T22:04:20.7297732Z 274            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-16T22:04:20.7297964Z 275            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-16T22:04:20.7298360Z 276            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-16T22:04:20.7298718Z 277            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-16T22:04:20.7299068Z 278            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
